*+
*  Name:
*     HSB_PAR

*  Purpose:
*     Define HSUB system parameter constants.

*  Language:
*     Starlink Fortran 77

*  Type of Module:
*     Global constants include file.

*  Description:
*     This file defines the size of any HSUB global constants.

*  Authors:
*     GJP: Grant Privett (STARLINK)
*     {enter_new_authors_here}

*  History:
*     04-NOV-1992 (GJP):
*        Original version.
*     {enter_further_changes_here}

*  Bugs:
*     {note_any_bugs_here}

